blog.title: Fake texts from last Might
blog.description: Things BNHA characters most definitely never said (sadly).

summary:
All Might : Let's spar, Young Midoriya. I want you to hit me with everything you got! Picture me as an enemy!
Midoriya Izuku :...
body:
All Might : Let's spar, Young Midoriya. I want you to hit me with everything you got! Picture me as an enemy!
Midoriya Izuku : Oh... I couldn't ever punch you, All Might!
All Might : Just picture me as someone you really hate, then!
Midoriya Izuku : That's an unhealthy way to deal with strained relationships, All Might!
All Might : ...fine. Just picture me as the economic crisis.
Midoriya Izuku : [punches through All Might's stomach at 100%]

blog.name: dubartz
blog.title: ☆▪DubArt▪☆
blog.description:
Hello!

Well, I'll start by saying that all the blogs I do will not have "Credits to the artist" 😱

Why is this happening? : 0

Actually I never notice the artists who do some work, gif or image. It may sound cruel and ugly but the truth is that I'm not interested😝

I'm sorry if they get mad at me for it but I want you to understand that I do not look for a lot of followers, did not look for fame, I do not look for likes or anything like that, I just want to share the photos that I love or mean something to me.🌠

This profile will have a variety of things, it can have quite romantic and beautiful things as well as it can have a variety of epic fights! I hope you enjoy the content: This will be in both Spanish and English⚘🔥

●Español:
"Hola!

Bueno, empezaré diciendo que todos los blogs que haga no tendrán "Créditos para el artista" 😱

¿Por qué está pasando esto? : 0

En realidad nunca me fijé en los artistas que hacen algún trabajo, gif o imagen. Puede sonar cruel y feo, pero la verdad es que no me interesa ...

Lo siento si se enojan conmigo por eso, pero quiero que entiendas que no busco muchos seguidores, no busqué fama, no busco "me gusta" ni nada de eso, solo quiero Comparte las fotos que amo o significan algo para mí.

¡Este perfil tendrá una variedad de cosas, puede tener cosas bastante románticas y hermosas, así como una variedad de luchas épicas! Espero que disfrutes el contenido: esto estará tanto en español como en inglés⚘🔥"

title: Top 5 OTP
body:
Hey guys, I was tagged in a game where we list our top 5 OTP and then tag 5 blogs. (P.S. I’m only doing anime ships because this is my anime blog)

I was tagged by @momokotuharumaki and you should go follow!

Here’s my top 5 in no particular order!! 

1. Izuocha (BNHA)

2. Ash x Eiji (Banana Fish)

3. Viktuuri (Yuri on Ice)

4. Kiribaku (BNHA)

5. Todomomo (BNHA)

Honestly I have so many so this was very hard. 

I tag @actuallyasweetpotato @izukumidochondrya @ignite-the-moonlight @yaomqmo and @deafmic
